# Power BI Dashboard - Operasyonel KPI Analizi
# Bu dosya Power BI Desktop'ta açılabilir

# Dashboard Bileşenleri:
# 1. Günlük/Haftalık Performans Metrikleri (Line Chart)
# 2. Process Efficiency Analizi (Funnel Chart)
# 3. Resource Utilization (Gauge Chart)
# 4. Quality Metrics (Bar Chart)
# 5. SLA Compliance (KPI Cards)

# Örnek Veri Yapısı:
# - Tarih
# - Process Type
# - Completion Time
# - Quality Score
# - Resource Used
# - SLA Target
# - SLA Actual
# - Error Count

# DAX Formülleri:
# Process Efficiency = [Completed Tasks] / [Total Tasks]
# SLA Compliance = [OnTimeDeliveries] / [TotalDeliveries]
# Quality Score = AVERAGE(Processes[QualityScore])
# Resource Utilization = [UsedResources] / [AvailableResources]

